# 🛒 Dahab Store App

Welcome to **Dahab Store**, a modern Store Management System built with **Flutter + Firebase**.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview
This app helps manage a shop easily and efficiently. It includes:
- 📦 Product Management
- 💰 Sales Tracking
- 📊 Dashboard Analytics
- 👥 User Management
- 🔐 Authentication System

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Flutter (Frontend)
- Firebase (Backend)
- Cloud Firestore (Database)
- Firebase Auth (Login System)

---

## ✨ Features
✔ Add / Edit / Delete Products  
✔ Track Daily Sales  
✔ Simple & Clean UI  
✔ Fast Performance  
✔ Mobile Friendly Design  

